				<td colspan="2"><span>I just bought EN1 wich is 10% more range. I noticed that gettin SC3 finnishes out the max extended range at +50% total. 
<br />

<br />
So my question is just how much is safe? The benefits of more range on the plus side are obvious, but I am not sure about the negative side.  Such as if im not pulling and its some what close quarters I dont want anything to hit say a monk when he is pulling and FD's.  I know I can stop the song depending on the situation, but you get the drift of what im trying to ask.
<br />

<br />
Just curious on everyones thoughts about this before I buy any more lvls of it. Thanks</span></td>
